# ============================================================
# PERSONAL DATA PROTECTION
# Everything below prevents private data from being pushed
# to the public mirror-palace repo.
# ============================================================

# --- People records (contain real names and relationship data) ---
# Block ALL .md files in status/people/ EXCEPT the templates
status/people/*.md

# --- Decisions (contain real decisions with context) ---
# Block all decision files (DEC-001.md, DEC-002.md, etc.)
status/decisions/DEC-*.md

# --- Filled-in domain status files ---
# These get populated with personal scores, notes, issues
# Block all .md in status/domains/ EXCEPT the template
status/domains/*.md

# --- Scan reports (contain analyzed personal data) ---
status/scan-report-*.md
status/scan-report*.md

# --- Agent memory files (contain observations about you) ---
agents/archetypes/*/MEMORY.md
agents/archetypes/*/WORKING.md

# --- Index files that get populated with personal data ---
status/ISSUE-INDEX.md
status/people/PEOPLE-INDEX.md
status/decisions/DECISIONS-INDEX.md

# --- Private sync/config docs ---
SYNC.md
*.private.md
*.local.md

# --- Catch-all: any file with "personal" or "private" in name ---
*personal*
*private*

# ============================================================
# SAFE FILES (these are general and OK to push public)
# ============================================================
# To push a file that matches a pattern above, use:
#   git add --force path/to/file.md
#
# Safe files that won't match the patterns above:
#   frameworks/         (all theory, templates, prompts, READMEs)
#   agents/_template/   (blank templates)
#   agents/archetypes/*/SOUL.md
#   agents/archetypes/*/README.md
#   agents/orchestration/
#   skills/
#   daily/              (blank templates)
#   guides/
#   examples/
#   docs/
#   index.md
#   README.md
#   CLAUDE.md
#   CONTRIBUTING.md
#   LICENSE
# ============================================================
